==Russian==

===Etymology===
''prefix'' [[胁褘-]] + ''root'' [[泻芯胁褘褉]] (''from'' [[泻芯胁褘褉褟褌褜]]) + [[-懈胁邪-]] + [[-褌褜]]

===Verb===
'''胁褘泻芯胁褘虂褉懈胁邪褌褜''' (vykov媒rivat') {{italbrac|imperfective|transitive}}

# to [[pick]] [[out]], to [[pluck]] [[out]], to [[take]] [[out]], to [[pull out]], to [[extract]] [[something|smth.]] while digging up, rummaging, delving.

